data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful single-family property located in a newly developed neighborhood. This cozy home is not just perfect for a first-time homebuyer but anyone that desires a newly built home without going through the building process. The Open concept living is so inviting perfect for hosting. All stainless-steel kitchen appliances will convey. Once you are on the second floor you have the convenience of a 2nd floor laundry room right next to the huge primary suite equipped with a walk-in closet and in-suite. This is definitely the property you've been looking for. Come check it out.
